# Chili Lime Black Bean Tacos

Based on [https://www.washingtonpost.com/recipes/...](https://www.washingtonpost.com/recipes/chili-lime-black-bean-tacos/17008) ([wayback](http://web.archive.org/web/20210203164149/https://www.washingtonpost.com/recipes/chili-lime-black-bean-tacos/17008))

